- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper discusses the distributed tracking on a land-based vehicle, which is a robotics application. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a distributed filter design that improves the estimation performance and relaxes the observability condition, which are relevant topics in artificial intelligence.
